  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_02_su_0004"> 
      
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">1.4&times;6을 계산하는 방법을 알아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>
 
        
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">1.4&times;6을 어림셈해 보고, 어떻게 어림셈했는지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="wrap">
            <div>
              <span class="gray_Box f32b" lang="y">답</span>
              <span class="input_wrap answer1 hint_right">
                <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="gray_Box f32b" lang="y">이유</span>
              <span class="input_wrap answer2">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y">1.5+1.5=3이므로 3×3=9 정도일 것 같습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">분수의 곱셈으로 나타내어 계산해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="fra_parens f32b">
              1.4×6=
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span class="input_wrap answer3">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
                </span>
                <span class="answer2">
                  10
                </span>
              </span> 
              ×6 =
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span class="input_wrap hint_80 answer4">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field> <span>×6</span>
                </span>
                <span class="answer2">
                  10
                </span>
              </span> 
              =
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span class="input_wrap answer5">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="84"></math-field>
                </span>
                <span class="answer2">10</span>
              </span>
              =
              <span class="input_wrap answer6">
                <math-field data-answer-single="8.4"></math-field>
              </span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">자연수의 곱셈으로 이용하여 계산해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box _524">
            <div class="wrapper flex f32b">
              <div class="box flex dir_col align_center">
                <div class="flex dir_row align_center">
                  <span class="bg_coral">14</span><span>x</span><span>6</span><span>=</span><span class="bg_sky">84</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex dir_row align_center f20b arrow-row">
                  <div class="flex align_center">
                    <span><img src="../../common_contents/img/ema524_01_SU/0004_arrow1.svg"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></div>
                    <span lang="y">배</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex align_center">
                    <span><img src="../../common_contents/img/ema524_01_SU/0004_arrow1.svg"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></div>
                    <span lang="y">배</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex dir_row align_center">
                  <span class="bg_coral">1.4</span><span>x</span><span>6</span><span>=</span><span class="bg_sky">8.4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="box flex justify_center align_center dir_row">
                <div class="fraction_box vertical-math">
                  <span class="bg_coral">1.4</span>
                  <span>x6</span>
                  <span>84</span>
                </div>
                <div class="f20b flex dir_col align_center arrow-col">
                  <div>
                    <div class="flex align_center justify_center">
                      <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></div>
                      <span lang="y">배</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="flex align_center justify_center">
                      <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></div>
                      <span lang="y">배</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fraction_box vertical-math">
                  <span class="bg_coral">1.4</span>
                  <span>x6</span>
                  <span class="input_wrap answer7">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="8.4"></math-field>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div> 
              <div class="message-bubble" lang="y">
                곱해지는 수가<br/>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>10</span>
                </span>
                배가 되면<br/> 곱도
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>10</span>
                </span>
                배가 돼.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <h3 lang="y">1.4×6의 계산 결과와 어림셈한 결과를 비교해 보고, (소수 한 자리 수)×(자연수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="wrap">
            <div>
              <span class="gray_Box f32b" lang="y">답</span>
              <span class="input_wrap example_left_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea" data-answer-single=""></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
